OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter baby girl falls from height
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after an 18-day-old baby
OL,8,Fgirl died after falling from a
OL,9,Fproperty in central London.
OL,11,FPolice were called to the scene at
OL,12,FHorseferry Road at around 7.30am on
OL,13,FSaturday following reports of a baby
OL,14,Ffalling from a height from a
OL,15,Fresidential property.
OL,17,FThe baby was taken to hospital, where
OL,18,Fshe was sadly pronounced dead, the
OL,19,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
