OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773540247
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter baby girl falls from height
OL,6,FA 43-year-old woman was arrested at
OL,7,Fthe scene on suspicion of murder. She
OL,8,Fwas taken into police custody, where
OL,9,Fshe remains, the force added.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Alison
OL,12,FFoxwell, who is leading the Met's
OL,13,Finvestigation, said: "Our thoughts
OL,14,Ftoday are with the baby's family.
OL,16,F"The death of an infant is always an
OL,17,Fextremely tragic occurrence, and
OL,18,Fofficers are making urgent enquiries
OL,19,Faround the circumstances.
